Released v1.5.0 - Enhanced Script Management & Modern UI of boshyxd/robloxstudio-mcp

Update plugin rbxmx file and store link for v1.5.0
- Updated MCPPlugin.rbxmx with latest UI improvements - Updated README with new Roblox Creator Store link - New store asset follows Roblox guidelines and won't be taken down

Remove gradient to fix button text visibility
- Remove UIGradient that was causing text to inherit background color - Use solid colors for better text contrast - Further reduce canvas size to 243 to eliminate remaining space - Ensure white text is clearly visible on solid button colors

Fix connect button text visibility and remove extra space
- Explicitly set button TextColor3 to white in both states - Reduce canvas size to 255 to eliminate empty space below button - Ensure white text is visible on both green and red button states

Fix final UI issues in plugin v1.5.0
- Replace emoji squares with readable text symbols (OK/X) - Remove extra space below connect button with fixed canvas size - Ensure button text remains white for good contrast

Modernize plugin UI design for v1.5.0
- Switch all fonts from SourceSans to Jura for modern look - Fix connect button contrast (green instead of blue-on-blue) - Update color scheme to darker grays with blue-purple gradients - Reduce spacing and section heights to eliminate extra space - Add diagonal gradients and improve visual hierarchy - Enhance input field styling with better borders
